meta.name: HP ProCurve Switch 2810-24G-Template
meta.description: template created from dashboard: HP ProCurve Switch 2810-24G

queries.text:
from(bucket: "telegraf")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "snmp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "sysUptime")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["agent_host"] == "192.168.2.254")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "telegraf")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "snmp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "hpLocalMemAllocBytes" or r["_field"] == "hpLocalMemTotalBytes")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["agent_host"] == "192.168.2.254")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    r with
    _value: r["hpLocalMemAllocBytes"] / r["hpLocalMemTotalBytes"] * 100.0
  }))
  |> yield(name: "mean")
